<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your agents are still reading your OOS</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f5f5f7;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.6;">
  <div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px;">

    <div style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:32px;">
      <div style="display:inline-block;padding:6px 12px;background:#0f766e;color:white;border-radius:6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;">OTP</div>
    </div>

    <h1 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 20px 0;line-height:1.3;">Your agents are still reading <%= publishedOosName ? publishedOosName : 'your OOS' %>.</h1>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">Your published OOS is doing its job. Every agent on your team that connects to OTP reads it before acting. The protocol is working in the background whether you are at the keyboard or not.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">But you have not been back in about <%= staleDays %> days. Coordination intelligence decays fast without a human reviewing it. The rules that earned trust three weeks ago may not match the team you are running today.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;font-size:16px;"><strong>A 5-minute check-in habit:</strong></p>

    <ul style="margin:0 0 24px 0;padding-left:22px;font-size:16px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/dashboard" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Open your dashboard</a> -- claim activity, similarity flags, what changed in your OOS this week</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/dashboard/oos-operating-plan" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Open your Operating Plan</a> -- the strategy layer above your OOS, push selected items into your OOS as structured claims</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:8px;"><a href="https://orgtp.com/browse" style="color:#0f766e;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Browse the network</a> -- what other orgs published this week that may be worth merging</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">If something specific is blocking you from coming back, hit reply. I read every message.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 32px 0;font-size:16px;">-- David Steel, founder</p>

    <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:32px 0;">

    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0 0 8px 0;">
      You are receiving this because you have an active account at orgtp.com.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0;">
      <a href="https://orgtp.com/api/v1/newsletter/unsubscribe/<%- encodeURIComponent(email) %>" style="color:#777;">Unsubscribe from re-engagement nudges</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
